videos.description: Eastern Michigan's Ty Groce drives to the basket for a one-handed layup, and draws a foul.
videos.headline: Groce makes layup and draws foul

videos.description: Buffalo's Jeremy Harris smashes a two-handed dunk to give the Bulls a 26-20 lead over the Eagles.
videos.headline: Harris comes up with two-handed slam

videos.description: CJ Massinburg crushes a dunk for Buffalo after a cross-court pass from Jayvon Graves.
videos.headline: Massinburg makes dunk unguarded

videos.description: Eastern Michigan's Paul Jackson cuts Buffalo's lead to 5 with a 3-pointer as the shot clock runs out.
videos.headline: Jackson sinks 3 at buzzer
